  "title": "Delivery App - General Instruction",
  "html_content": "<main class=\"SuperHubDoc3Z-1XSVTg-Q1 rm-Guides\" id=\"content\"><div class=\"SuperHubDoc-container2RY1FPE4Ewze rm-Container rm-Container_flex\"><article class=\"SuperHubDoc-article3ArTrEavUTKg rm-Article rm-Guides-SuperHub\"><div class=\"grid-container-fluid\" id=\"content-container\"><section class=\"content-body grid-75\"><div class=\"rm-Markdown markdown-body rm-Markdown markdown-body ng-non-bindable\" data-testid=\"RDMD\" style=\"margin-left:31px\"><h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"install-abivin-vroute-mobile-app\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Install Abivin vRoute Mobile app</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Install Abivin vRoute Mobile app\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#install-abivin-vroute-mobile-app\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The Abivin vRoute Mobile app is available for both iOS and Android systems</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"heading heading-3 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-text\">Download Mobile app on iOS</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Download Mobile app on iOS\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#download-mobile-app-on-ios\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>You can download Abivin vRoute v3.0 mobile app for iOS from this link: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/vn/app/abivin-vroute-v3-0/id1314836746\" target=\"_self\"><strong>Abivin vRoute for iOS</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"1920\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/8f10934-DGF5Omqw27.png\" title=\"DGF5Omqw27.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<h3 class=\"heading heading-3 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-text\">Download Mobile app on Android</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Download Mobile app on Android\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#download-mobile-app-on-android\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>You can download Abivin vRoute v3.0 mobile app for Android from this link: Abivin vRoute for Android</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"1920\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/08e3a17-om2Z9LEtKq.png\" title=\"om2Z9LEtKq.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"login-abivin-vroute-mobile-app\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Login Abivin vRoute Mobile app</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Login Abivin vRoute Mobile app\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#login-abivin-vroute-mobile-app\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>After you have successfully installed the Abivin vRoute Mobile app, the app icon will appear on the screen. To open the app, tap on its icon</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"login-with-username-and-password\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Login with Username and Password</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Login with Username and Password\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#login-with-username-and-password\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>After tapping on the app icon, the <strong>Sign In</strong> screen will appear. You have to enter the <em><strong>Username</strong></em> and <em><strong>Password</strong></em> provided by the administrator, then tap on <strong>Sign In</strong> button</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"420\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/491a334-phone_screen.png\" title=\"phone screen.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"login-with-fingerprint\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Login with fingerprint</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Login with fingerprint\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#login-with-fingerprint\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>This is an easy, timesaving way to log in to your account, using only your fingerprint</li>\n<li>To log in with your fingerprint, first you will have to enable that feature</li>\n<li>Log in with your Username and Password as described above</li>\n<li>Access the setting section <a href=\"https://docs.abivin.com/docs/mobile-app-general-instruction#section-access-the-app-settings\" target=\"_self\"><strong>(Tutorial can be seen here)</strong></a></li>\n<li>Scroll down the Settings screen, then tap on the toggle icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-toggle-off\"></i> under the text <strong>Fingerprint</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"415\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/278114c-finger.png\" title=\"finger.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>A form that reads <strong>Enter your current password</strong> will pop out. You will need to input your current password, then tap on <strong>Done</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"314\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/cd8e535-enter_current_pass.png\" title=\"enter current pass.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>After you have successfully input your password, that icon will change to <i class=\"fa-regular fa-toggle-on\"></i>, that means this feature has been enabled</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"419\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/9b081a1-finger_enabled.png\" title=\"finger enabled.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>Now you can log in to your account by tapping on the fingerprint icon on the log in screen. Then, tap your fingerprint on the home button of your mobile device, the same as when you unlock your device screen</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"816\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/aed2c77-finger_log_in.png\" title=\"finger log in.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"access-the-app-settings\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Access the app settings</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Access the app settings\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#access-the-app-settings\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>After you have logged in to your account, you can access the settings of the app by tapping on the User icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-user\"></i> on the top right of the screen, then tap on <strong>Settings</strong> <i class=\"fa-regular fa-cog\"></i> text</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"839\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/3f289ea-9c315bb-acc_setting.png\" title=\"9c315bb-acc_setting.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"update-strong-password\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Update Strong password</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Update Strong password\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#update-strong-password\"></a></h2>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"update-password-within-mobile-app-settings\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Update password within Mobile app settings</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Update password within Mobile app settings\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#update-password-within-mobile-app-settings\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Access the setting section <a href=\"https://docs.abivin.com/docs/mobile-app-general-instruction#section-access-the-app-settings\" target=\"_self\"><strong>(Tutorial can be seen here)</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"839\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/9c315bb-acc_setting.png\" title=\"acc setting.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>Scroll down the Settings screen, you will see a blue <strong>Change Password</strong> button</li>\n<li>Tap on that button, you will be navigated to the <strong>Change Password</strong> screen</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"834\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/c63176c-change_pass.png\" title=\"change pass.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>Input your current password into the <strong>Current password</strong> field, then input your new password into the <strong>New password</strong> and <strong>Verify password</strong> fields</li>\n<li>As you type the new password, the Mobile app will perform checking to measure your password strength according to our <a href=\"https://docs.abivin.com/docs/mobile-app-general-instruction#section-password-rules\" target=\"_self\"><strong>Password rules</strong></a>. Your new password will only be accepted once all the criteria have been met</li>\n<li>After your new password has passed the criteria, tap on the blue <strong>Change Password</strong> button</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"420\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/4d31da4-new_pass.png\" title=\"new pass.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>A pop up will display, announcing that you have successfully changed your password to a new, strong password. At the same time, you will be logged out of your account. You will have to log in again using the recently created strong password</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"update-password-when-logging-in\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Update password when logging in</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Update password when logging in\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#update-password-when-logging-in\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>As we periodically roll out the Strong password feature to our clients, users on Mobile app who still use weak passwords will not be able to perform anything unless they change their passwords to stronger ones</li>\n<li>The Mobile app will immediately navigate to the <strong>Change password</strong> screen after logging in</li>\n<li>The process to change weak password to strong password is similar as above</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"password-rules\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Password rules</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Password rules\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#password-rules\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>A strong password will help your organization protect privacy, prevent cyber attacks and data theft. Therefore, we have employed a rigorous set of rules to ensure threats are as minimal as possible</li>\n<li>A strong password is one that complies with the following rules</li>\n<li><strong>Rule #1</strong>. Contains uppercase letters</li>\n<li><strong>Rule #2</strong>. Contains lowercase letters</li>\n<li><strong>Rule #3</strong>. Contains numbers</li>\n<li><strong>Rule #4</strong>. Contains at least one special characters (Characters that are not numbers and letters, including ! \" # $ % &amp; ' ( ) * + , - . / : ; &lt; = &gt; ? @ [ \\ ] ^ _ ` { | } ~ \" and spaces)</li>\n<li><strong>Rule #5</strong>. Is at least eight characters long</li>\n<li>As you input the password, the checklist below will help you see what rules you have met. Rules that have been met will have the corresponding icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-check-circle\"></i> turn from gray to green</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"693\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/37b2487-pass.png\" title=\"pass.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"reset-password-when-forgotten\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Reset password when forgotten</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Reset password when forgotten\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#reset-password-when-forgotten\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>In case you forgot your password, on the login screen, you can tap on the <strong>Forgot password</strong> text below the <strong>Sign In</strong> button. You will be navigated to the <strong>Forgot password</strong> screen</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"835\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/7a44361-forgot_pass.png\" title=\"forgot pass.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>Type your Username into the <strong>Username</strong> field, then tap on the blue <strong>Email me a recovery link</strong> button</li>\n<li>You will be navigated to the <strong>Recover Password</strong> screen. At the same time Abivin vRoute will automatically send an instruction email to your email address. In the email, you will see a <em><strong>Verify Code</strong></em></li>\n<li>In case you haven't received the instruction email, tap on <strong>Resend Email</strong> text</li>\n</ul>\n<figure><span aria-label=\"588\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"588\" class=\"img img-align-center border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/c22f509-change_pass_email.png\" title=\"change pass email.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/><figcaption><p>Recovery email</p></figcaption></span></span></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>Type that code into the <strong>Verify Code</strong> field, then tap on the blue <strong>Change Password</strong> button</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"420\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/a02130e-change_forgot.png\" title=\"change forgot.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>You will be navigated to the <strong>Recover Password</strong> screen. Here you can input the new password. The process to create a new password is similar to how you change password above</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"get-real-time-support\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Get real time support</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Get real time support\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#get-real-time-support\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>To get real time support from our Customer Service department, please follow the steps below</li>\n<li>Tap on your user icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-user\"></i> on the top right of the screen, then tap on the orange conversation icon at the bottom of the panel</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"824\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/f2aa85d-converse.png\" title=\"converse.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>You will be directed to the <strong>Conversations</strong> screen. Tap on on the appropriate language (We currently have two channels in English and Vietnamese)</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"420\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/ca6bee2-conversation.png\" title=\"conversation.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>Begin the conversation by inputting your query in the field with the text <strong>Type a message</strong>. After you have finished the query, tap on the icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-paper-plane\"></i> to send your query. Our Customer Service department will get in touch with you shortly</li>\n<li>If you want to attach a picture to describe your query more thoroughly, tap on the paperclip icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-paperclip\"></i>. You can take a picture or upload a picture from your mobile device</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"420\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/f9ca18e-send_mes.png\" title=\"send mes.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span></div><div class=\"UpdatedAt\"><p class=\"DateLine\"><i class=\"icon icon-watch\"></i>Updated<!-- --> <!-- -->about 1 month ago<!-- --> </p></div><hr class=\"NextStepsDivider\"/></section><section class=\"content-toc grid-25\"></section></div><div class=\"ModalWrapper\" id=\"tutorialmodal-root\"></div></article></div></main>",
